<div class="pricing-questions">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>What is an active behavior?</h3>

      <p>An active behavior is a single behavior that runs on a single repository. For example 10 behaviors could be the same behavior running on 10 different repositories or 10 different behaviors active on a single repository.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Do you offer discounts?</h3>

      <p>We don't have anything formalized just yet, but if you are in education, open source or non-profit please shoot us an email with your usecase and we'll see how we can help you out!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Is my code safe?</h3>

      <p>Please see our <a href="/security">security page</a> to learn more about the extensive measures we take to ensure that your code is kept private, sandboxed, and safe.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>I have another question</h3>

      <p>Great! Please email us and we'll be happy to answer any other questions you have about Pushbit.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
